    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project car or a budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine is functional, though it may require some minor mechanical attention soon, and the transmission shifts as expected for its age. Cosmetically, there are several noticeable scratches, minor dents on the body, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear and staining. While it isn't perfect, it is a reliable enough option for those looking for affordable transportation.",
      "price": 21500.0,
